由於失重狀態增加了上半身的體液量，太空人會經歷到[[顱內壓|顱內壓]]的增加。這會造成眼球後方的壓力增加，影響到眼球形狀並且輕微地擠壓到[[視神經|視神經]]。<ref name="NYT-20140127" /><ref name="Mader-2011">{{cite journal |author=Mader, T. H. et al. |title=Optic Disc Edema, Globe Flattening, Choroidal Folds, and Hyperopic Shifts Observed in Astronauts after Long-duration Space Flight |url=http://www.ophsource.org/periodicals/ophtha/article/S0161-6420(11)00564-1/abstract Oph |year=2011 |journal={{tsl|en|Ophthalmology (journal)||Ophthalmology (journal)}} |volume=118 |issue=10 |pages=2058–2069 |doi=10.1016/j.ophtha.2011.06.021 |pmid=21849212}}</ref><ref name="Puiu-20111109">{{cite web |last=Puiu |first=Tibi |title=Astronauts’ vision severely affected during long space missions |url=http://www.zmescience.com/medicine/astronaut-eyesight-damage-weightlessness-3214143/ |date=November 9, 2011 |publisher=zmescience.com |accessdate=February 9, 2012 |archive-date=2011-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213062133/http://www.zmescience.com/medicine/astronaut-eyesight-damage-weightlessness-3214143/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CNN-20120109">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/video/#/video/us/2012/02/09/pkg-zarrella-astronaut-vision.cnn |title=Male Astronauts Return With Eye Problems (video) |date=9 February 2012 |publisher=CNN News |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archive-date=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5vLKURN8r?url=http://www.cnn.com/video/#/video/us/2012/02/09/pkg-zarrella-astronaut-vision.cnn |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Space-20120313">{{cite web |author=Space Staff |title=Spaceflight Bad for Astronauts' Vision, Study Suggests |url=http://www.space.com/14876-astronaut-spaceflight-vision-problems.html |date=13 March 2012 |publisher={{tsl|en|Space.com||Space.com}} |accessdate=14 March 2012 |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106180914/https://www.space.com/14876-astronaut-spaceflight-vision-problems.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Radiology-20120313">{{cite journal |author=Kramer, Larry A. et al. |title=Orbital and Intracranial Effects of Microgravity: Findings at 3-T MR Imaging |url=http://radiology.rsna.org/content/early/2012/03/07/radiol.12111986.abstract?sid=8682af1e-b07f-4ad9-8453-ee319bad639e |journal={{tsl|en|Radiology (journal)||Radiology (journal)}} |doi=10.1148/radiol.12111986 |date=13 March 2012 |accessdate=14 March 2012 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213030150/http://radiology.rsna.org/content/early/2012/03/07/radiol.12111986.abstract?sid=8682af1e-b07f-4ad9-8453-ee319bad639e |dead-url=no }}</ref>  這個現象在2012年，對於待在太空中至少一個月的太空人返回地球後用[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]進行研究之後被注意到。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.discovery.com/space/eye-problems-astronauts-120313.html |title=Eye Problems Common in Astronauts |date=13 March 2012 |publisher=Discovery News |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427172831/http://news.discovery.com/space/eye-problems-astronauts-120313.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>如此的視力問題可能成為包括前往[[火星|火星]]的[[載人太空|載人太空]]等未來深空航行任務的主要事務。<ref name="WIRED-20140212" /><ref name="Mader-2011" /><ref name="Puiu-20111109" /><ref name="CNN-20120109" /><ref name="Space-20120313" />

